.SH "[BRIDGEVLAN] SECTION OPTIONS"
.PP
The [BridgeVLAN] section manages the VLAN ID configurations of a bridge master or port, and accepts the following keys\&. To make the settings in this section take an effect,
\fIVLANFiltering=\fR
