\fBsystemd.netdev\fR(5)\&. If at least one valid settings specified in this section in a \&.network file for an interface, all assigned VLAN IDs on the interface that are not configured in the \&.network file will be removed\&. If VLAN IDs on an interface need to be managed by other tools, then the settings in this section cannot be used in the matching \&.network file\&.
.PP
\fIVLAN=\fR
.RS 4
